{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/76/7650.jpg","floor":"#1","group":"靠谱人生茶话会","groupHref":"/group/boring","groupThumb":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/icon/m/000/00/03/364.jpg","message":"<img src=\"https://www.nasa.gov/sites/default/files/thumbnails/image/niac2017_phase_i_heidi_fearn.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><a href=\"https://www.nasa.gov/directorates/spacetech/niac/2018_Phase_I_Phase_II/Mach_Effect_for_In_Space_Propulsion_Interstellar_Mission\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://www.nasa.gov/directorate ... nterstellar_Mission</a><br>和<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/group/topic/343814\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">之前提的EmDrive</a>一样，马赫效应推进器也不需要推进剂就能产生推力。<br><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Woodward_effect\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Woodward_effect</a><br><br>工作原理类似武侠高手踏空而行，利用时空涟漪的波动，收脚和踏脚时质量不同而产生推力达到踏空而行的武学。<br>马赫效应通过压电震动来模拟这一效应，震动来回的力差产生推力而达到空间推进的效果。目前理论和技术已经成熟，星际飞行可在十年内实现。<br>各种推进和能源技术近期不断涌现，宇宙星际大航海时代即将开启。<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"> ","time":"2018-4-2 04:16","title":"NASA又一黑科技，马赫效应推进器打造星舰和星际之门","userId":"iiiiuuuu","userName":"完全没有","userSign":"(就是没有)"}